Java RMI Client Server
-------------------


Requirments: Latest jdk and jre modules which can support java applet, swing, awt and RMI

Compilation: Open the directory where all the codes are stored
             javac *.java

Execution: 

Server Side:
	   In one terminal start the server with
           java Server

Client Side:
           Each client will run as a new process
           Each time a client has to be run

           java Client

           The first message prompted will ask for the client name
           The second message will ask for the server IP address

           All the message in the chat will be broadcast
           /list will show the list of all the users
           /exit will quit the user

